HEADWORD: Theban
<hw>The"ban</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Thebanus</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to Thebes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Theban year</b></col> <fld>(Anc. Chron.)</fld>, <cd>the
Egyptian year of 365 days and 6 hours.</cd> <au>J. Bryant.</au></cs>⟦br⟧
