==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Theban
<hw>The"ban</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A native or inhabitant of Thebes;
also, a wise man.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I'll talk a word with this same learned <qex>Theban</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

